  "summary": "neural-network-scan exfiltrates host information to attacker-controlled C2",
  "details": "The package ships collect.js, which imports child_process, fs, os, http, and https, gathers host identifiers (os.hostname(), os.homedir()) along with filesystem reconnaissance (fs.existsSync probes), and POSTs the collected data to the hardcoded endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The combination of system-info collection, filesystem enumeration, and a hardcoded non-publisher HTTP destination receiving a POST is the canonical exfiltration shape. The destination domain is unrelated to any legitimate `neural-network-scan` purpose and is an attacker-controlled C2.",
